separation costs, a charge of $312 associated with employee separation costs, a charge of $42 related to the impairment of certain european manufacturing assets, a charge of $23 related to the
shutdown of manufacturing assets at a u.s. facility, a charge of $29 to write off abandoned technology, a charge of $27 to reflect a decline in the value of an investment security, and a charge of $45
to establish a reserve in connection with the pfoa class action litigation case in west virginia.
